解唔買option?"},{"pid":"4a834457aa9e9e59fbbfb0ade6426a9ee16000bc","tid":2391443,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3d431117cd4a1bb2154188b49d4aa43a56bd0ecd","tid":2391443,"uid":368287,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T08:40:14.000Z","msg":"真係好好奇同埋奇怪<br />\n明明option槓桿上黎好似差唔多(?)<br />\n但又唔會打靶 <br />\n市場點解仲會流通牛熊證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:28:33.000Z","msg":"牛熊依D垃圾得香港D傻仔先會玩既姐<br />\n美股邊會有牛熊?<br />\n<br />\n就好似炒股既明明都係賭錢 但佢地會睇唔起賭波賭馬既人<br />\n炒option既明明都係賭錢 但佢地會睇唔起炒牛熊既人"},{"pid":"9b24b201dccb6de466dd46a17a30d1d4ed1eff1c","tid":2391443,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"得hk 先有牛熊咋嘛，仲要食你夾棍"},{"pid":"bd37382dfdbe055df968cbee3409d43bc4084e35","tid":2391443,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b24b201dccb6de466dd46a17a30d1d4ed1eff1c","tid":2391443,"uid":57462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"得hk 先有牛熊咋嘛，仲要食你夾棍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:31:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼佬都有，叫turbo warrant"},{"pid":"45ae15cd124826badfb3f08aab1321630f1edb55","tid":2391443,"uid":41923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-02T10:31:51.000Z","msg":"好簡單<br />\n<br />\n1. 99%散戶都係弱智<br />\n2. 牛熊夠簡單+容易買+較容易理解<br />\n3. 重點：券商唔當牛熊係衍生工具，可以用股票戶口買賣，但option唔可以用股票戶口買賣<br />\n<br />\n我相信上面三個point已經有連燈仔覺得too long dont read，加上用開支牛既連燈仔唔會明第3點，所以再次印證第1點散戶99%都係弱智。"}]}